// ============================================================================
// USAGE NOTES
// ============================================================================
//
// PURCHASE FLOW:
// 1. User browses TrainingProduct catalog
// 2. User adds product to cart (applies DiscountCode if any)
// 3. Stripe payment creates TrainingPurchase
// 4. On successful payment, CourseEnrollment(s) created with access
// 5. User can access course content
// 6. Certificate generated on completion
// 7. CPD hours logged to CPDLog
//
// INTERACTIVE LEARNING:
// 1. User progresses through CourseLesson
// 2. Encounters InteractiveElement (quiz, scenario, etc.)
// 3. User responds, creates InteractiveResponse
// 4. System provides immediate feedback
// 5. Tracks engagement and completion
//
// CERTIFICATE GENERATION:
// 1. User completes all course requirements
// 2. System generates Certificate from CertificateTemplate
// 3. Certificate includes verification code and QR code
// 4. Certificate downloadable as PDF
// 5. CPD hours logged automatically
//
// ============================================================================
